                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 259.) I was in the station—the prisoner said, "I have taken the money; three sovereigns are in my box, and two I have spent"—I then went to No. 4, Waterloo-street, broke a box open, and found three sovereigns in it.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
